One nice bonus is that they have a computer with free internet access right off the lobby, allowing us to check in on our email without having to find and pay for an internet cafe.	During the check-in the staff was professional, they were quick (anyway, I missed some small personal something) and then we have been shown our room: a beautiful room with authentic furniture.	Hotel staff are very well trained, especially at the front desk where the check in and reception staff are efficient and knowledgable with a very friendly disposition.	When we mentioned that our booking included a free bottle of wine it was delivered to our door within minutes.